{"componentChunkName":"component---src-layouts-blog-post-layout-js","path":"/blog/simple-theme-product-page-slideshow-tutorial","result":{"pageContext":{"id":1543,"date":"2022-04-11T10:16:51","date_gmt":"2022-04-11T10:16:51","guid":{"rendered":"https://www.ezfy.club/?p=1543"},"modified":"2022-04-11T10:51:37","modified_gmt":"2022-04-11T10:51:37","slug":"simple-theme-product-page-slideshow-tutorial","status":"publish","type":"post","link":"https://www.ezfy.club/simple-theme-product-page-slideshow-tutorial/","title":{"rendered":"Simple Theme: how to add a slideshow with arrows to product images"},"content":{"rendered":"\n<p>As the name suggests, the Simple theme is, undoubtedly, one of the best themes out there for merchants looking for a minimalistic yet persuading design. However, the major flaw of the Simple theme is that it does not come with many customization options out of the box for its product page, especially lacking swiping and arrows for the product images.<br><br>In this tutorial I&#8217;ll teach you step-by-step how to upgrade your Simple theme&#8217;s product page by adding arrows, infinite loop, thumbnails carousel and much more. <br><br><a href=\"https://plugins-password-is-123.myshopify.com/products/flex-bag\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">Here is a live preview</a> of how the end result will look like. (Password: <strong>123</strong>)<br><br>Please download the files clicking <a href=\"https://ezfycode.com/shop/simple-theme-slider-pro\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">here</a>.</p>\n\n\n\n<h3 id=\"h-making-a-backup-of-your-theme\">Making a backup of your theme</h3>\n\n\n\n<p>Before diving into the tutorial make sure you download the theme, so in case you face any issues you can easily revert back.<br><br><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"1514\" height=\"481\" class=\"wp-image-503\" style=\"width: 600px;\" src=\"https://www.ezfy.club/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/dl-123.png\" alt=\"\" srcset=\"https://www.ezfy.club/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/dl-123.png 1514w, https://www.ezfy.club/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/dl-123-600x191.png 600w, https://www.ezfy.club/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/dl-123-1200x381.png 1200w, https://www.ezfy.club/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/dl-123-768x244.png 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1514px) 100vw, 1514px\" /></p>\n\n\n\n<h3 id=\"h-getting-ready-and-downloading-the-code-files\">Getting ready and downloading the code files</h3>\n\n\n\n<ol><li>In your Shopify admin, go to <strong>Online Store</strong> > <strong>Themes </strong>> <strong>Actions </strong>> <strong>Edit Code</strong>.</li><li>After <a href=\"https://ezfycode.com/shop/simple-theme-slider-pro\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">downloading the code files</a>, inside of the downloaded .zip, find the following file: <br><br><strong>product-template.txt</strong></li></ol>\n\n\n\n<h3 id=\"h-setting-up-the-product-template-txt-file\">Setting up the product-template.txt file</h3>\n\n\n\n<ol><li>Open the <strong>product-template.txt </strong>file and copy all the code in there.</li><li>Go back to yout Shopify admin, find the <strong>product-template.liquid</strong> file in your theme. (please make sure it is exactly <strong>product-template.liquid</strong>. <strong>product.liquid</strong> is a different file).</li><li>Delete everything in there, paste the code that you copied &amp; save.</li><li>That is it! Your slideshow is now working and ready to use.</li></ol>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large\"><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"1200\" height=\"567\" src=\"https://www.ezfy.club/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/product-1-1200x567.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-1165\" srcset=\"https://www.ezfy.club/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/product-1-1200x567.jpg 1200w, https://www.ezfy.club/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/product-1-850x401.jpg 850w, https://www.ezfy.club/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/product-1-768x363.jpg 768w, https://www.ezfy.club/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/product-1.jpg 1207w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1200px) 100vw, 1200px\" /></figure>\n\n\n\n<h3 id=\"h-customizing-your-new-slideshow-to-your-liking\">Customizing your new slideshow to your liking</h3>\n\n\n\n<ol><li>From your Shopify admin, navigate to&nbsp;<strong>Online Store</strong>&nbsp;&gt;&nbsp;<strong>Themes&nbsp;</strong>&gt;<strong>Customize</strong>.<br><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"1699\" height=\"751\" class=\"wp-image-570\" style=\"width: 600px;\" src=\"https://www.ezfy.club/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/customize123.jpg\" alt=\"Accessing the customize page on Shopify admin\" srcset=\"https://www.ezfy.club/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/customize123.jpg 1699w, https://www.ezfy.club/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/customize123-600x265.jpg 600w, https://www.ezfy.club/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/customize123-1200x530.jpg 1200w, https://www.ezfy.club/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/customize123-768x339.jpg 768w, https://www.ezfy.club/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/customize123-1536x679.jpg 1536w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1699px) 100vw, 1699px\" /></li><li>On the top, from the dropdown options, select <strong>product pages</strong> &gt; <strong>default product</strong>. <br><br>Once this page loads, click on <strong>product pages</strong> on the left.<br><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"804\" height=\"485\" class=\"wp-image-632\" style=\"width: 600px;\" src=\"https://www.ezfy.club/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/prod1.jpg\" alt=\"\" srcset=\"https://www.ezfy.club/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/prod1.jpg 804w, https://www.ezfy.club/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/prod1-600x362.jpg 600w, https://www.ezfy.club/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/prod1-768x463.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 804px) 100vw, 804px\" /></li><li>Inside the <strong>Product pages</strong> menu you&#8217;ll find all available options for the Simple Slider.</li></ol>\n\n\n\n<h3 id=\"h-something-went-wrong-there-is-a-bug-or-i-can-t-install-it\">Something went wrong, there is a bug or I can&#8217;t install it</h3>\n\n\n\n<p>No worries at all! We&#8217;ll be more than happy to help you out. <br><br>Just please send us an email at <strong>ezfycode@gmail.com</strong> with your website URL and we&#8217;ll get back to you on the same day to assist you and get it installed.</p>\n","protected":false},"excerpt":{"rendered":"<p>Simple guide to add swiping, arrows, thumbnail carousel and much more to your Simple theme&#8217;s product page.</p>\n","protected":false},"author":1,"featured_media":1549,"comment_status":"open","ping_status":"open","sticky":false,"template":"","format":"standard","meta":[],"categories":[9],"tags":[154,384],"image_alt":"","acf":[],"featured_image_src":"https://www.ezfy.club/wp-content/uploads/2022/04/title-above-850x478.png","featured_image_small_src":"https://www.ezfy.club/wp-content/uploads/2022/04/title-above-200x200.png","featured_image_large_src":"https://www.ezfy.club/wp-content/uploads/2022/04/title-above-1200x675.png","post_count":null,"categories_names":["Blog"],"tag_names":["Code Tutorial","simple theme"],"_links":{"self":[{"href":"https://www.ezfy.club/json/wp/v2/posts/1543"}],"collection":[{"href":"https://www.ezfy.club/json/wp/v2/posts"}],"about":[{"href":"https://www.ezfy.club/json/wp/v2/types/post"}],"author":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https://www.ezfy.club/json/wp/v2/users/1"}],"replies":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https://www.ezfy.club/json/wp/v2/comments?post=1543"}],"version-history":[{"count":6,"href":"https://www.ezfy.club/json/wp/v2/posts/1543/revisions"}],"predecessor-version":[{"id":1555,"href":"https://www.ezfy.club/json/wp/v2/posts/1543/revisions/1555"}],"wp:featuredmedia":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https://www.ezfy.club/json/wp/v2/media/1549"}],"wp:attachment":[{"href":"https://www.ezfy.club/json/wp/v2/media?parent=1543"}],"wp:term":[{"taxonomy":"category","embeddable":true,"href":"https://www.ezfy.club/json/wp/v2/categories?post=1543"},{"taxonomy":"post_tag","embeddable":true,"href":"https://www.ezfy.club/json/wp/v2/tags?post=1543"}],"curies":[{"name":"wp","href":"https://api.w.org/{rel}","templated":true}]